# SPA fallback: every path with no matching static file renders the app shell.
# NOTE: do NOT add explicit /terms -> /terms.html or /privacy -> /privacy.html
# rewrites here. Cloudflare Pages serves static files first and exposes them at
# their extensionless URL automatically (/privacy.html is reachable at /privacy),
# and it 308-redirects /privacy.html -> /privacy on its own. An explicit
# /privacy -> /privacy.html rewrite fights that auto-redirect and causes an
# infinite 308 loop. Static-first + the catch-all below is all that's needed.
/*    /index.html   200
